ðŸ”¹ Correct Order

Initialize project (one time):

docker run -it -v $(pwd):/app -w /app rasa/rasa:3.6.21-full init --no-prompt


Train your model (optional, rasa init trains a default model):

docker run -it -v $(pwd):/app -w /app rasa/rasa:3.6.21-full train


Run Rasa server:

docker run -it -v $(pwd):/app -w /app -p 5005:5005 rasa/rasa:3.6.21-full run --enable-api


Run Action Server (custom actions):

docker run -it -v $(pwd):/app -w /app -p 5055:5055 rasa/rasa-sdk:latest run actions
